  "design_notes": "The Medium difficulty chart for this 130 BPM song perfectly translates per-bar energy into rhythmic density. Drops are mapped to comfortable, flowing 8th-note runs (stream/steps textures) with crossovers restricted to light body turns, while breaks and intros feature sparser 4th-note tapping and holds that match the vocal or synth sustains. No gaps exist between the tiled phrases, and holds comprise ~6.3% of the total notes, fully complying with StepMania pad-play ergonomics.",
